article_title: Medicaid expansion forum set for Tuesday
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Showers possible.

Tonight

Cloudy with a few showers. Thunder possible. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

og.description: CASPER – A group that wants the Wyoming Legislature to expand Medicaid to 20,000 low-income adults will hold panel discussions on the benefits of the Obamacare program Tuesday in Cheyenne
